original_title: Judy Collins & Jonas Fjeld - Winter Stories: Live From the Oslo Opera House
overview: Judy Collins - along with critically acclaimed Norwegian folk artist Jonas Fjeld and masterful Americana band Chatham County Line - invite you to a hootenanny at the Oslo Opera House. Filmed in February 2020 off the tails of the newly formed groups' critically-acclaimed studio release “Winter Stories.”
title: Judy Collins & Jonas Fjeld - Winter Stories: Live From the Oslo Opera House
